OL,6,FThe Sheffield-based national suicide
OL,7,Fprevention charity, The Baton of Hope,
OL,8,Fhas announced plans to stage another
OL,9,Ftour of the UK in 2025.
OL,11,FThe charity launched it's first tour
OL,12,Flast year, which saw almost 1000
OL,13,Fpeople bereaved by suicide carried a
OL,14,Fbaton through 12 cities in 12 days.
