OL,3,CAlastair Campbell opens up on mental
OL,4,Chealth at charity conference
OL,6,FThe news of a second tour was
OL,7,Fannounced at a conference in
OL,8,FSheffield, which was hosted by Prof
OL,9,FRory O'Connor, President of the
OL,10,FInternational Association for Suicide
OL,11,FPrevention, as well as mental health
OL,12,Fcampaigner Alastair Campbell.
OL,14,FDuring the conference, the former
OL,15,Fjournalist and spokesman for Tony
OL,16,FBlair spoke openly about his own
OL,17,Fstruggles with mental health and
OL,18,Fsuicidal thoughts.
