OL,3,CAlastair Campbell opens up on mental
OL,4,Chealth at charity conference
OL,6,FHe said: "Obviously I'm sitting here
OL,7,Fand I'm talking and breathing and I've
OL,8,Fnever taken my own life, but I've been
OL,9,Fclose a few times and I understand the
OL,10,Fmotivations that take people to that
OL,11,Fultimate place where they decided that
OL,12,Fdeath is preferable to life.
OL,14,F"I just feel that as a country we
OL,15,Fcan't really call ourselves civilised
OL,16,Fwhen we have so many people that are
OL,17,Fstruggling and there just isn't the
OL,18,Fsupport for them.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
