OL,3,CAlastair Campbell opens up on mental
OL,4,Chealth at charity conference
OL,6,F"Families can do so much, friends can
OL,7,Fdo so much but ultimately it's about
OL,8,Fstripping down the attitudes so that
OL,9,Fwe're just as open about mental health
OL,10,Fas we are about physical health.
OL,12,F"But above all, that when people are
OL,13,Fin genuine crisis, there are systems
OL,14,Fof support in place there that will
OL,15,Fprevent them from that final awful
OL,16,Fstep that ends their lives and
OL,17,Fdestroys the lives of so many other
OL,18,Fpeople."
