OL,6,FThe conference took place in Sheffield
OL,7,Fto coincide with Mental Health
OL,8,FAwareness Week and brought together
OL,9,Fsome of the nation's most influential
OL,10,Fmental health campaigners, including
OL,11,FThe Baton of Hope's co-founder Mike
OL,12,FMcCarthy.
OL,14,FMike McCarthy founded the suicide
OL,15,Fprevention charity after his son Ross
OL,16,Ftragically took his own life in 2021.
