OL,3,CAlastair Campbell opens up on mental
OL,4,Chealth at charity conference
OL,6,FRoss McCarthy had been struggling with
OL,7,Fhis mental health for years, but his
OL,8,Ffather Mike said that the problem was
OL,9,Fexacerbated by the isolation caused by
OL,10,Fthe lockdown.
OL,12,FHe was 31 when he died and left behind
OL,13,Fa fiancee and three-year-old son.
OL,15,FRoss McCarthy left a message behind
OL,16,Fasking his family to campaign for
OL,17,Fbetter mental health support.
