OL,6,FThe charity's first baton tour in 2023
OL,7,Fwas hailed by Prime Minister Rishi
OL,8,FSunak as the biggest suicide
OL,9,Fprevention initiative the country had
OL,10,Fever seen.
OL,12,FMike McCarthy said: "We have already
OL,13,Fhad many emails from towns and cities
OL,14,Fasking how they can get involved with
OL,15,Fthe next tour and that's despite not
OL,16,Fhaving made anything public.
