OL,3,CAlastair Campbell opens up on mental
OL,4,Chealth at charity conference
OL,6,F"Based on last year's tour this will
OL,7,Fbe an incredible opportunity it's to
OL,8,Fmake sure the subject of suicide is no
OL,9,Flonger swept under the carpet and for
OL,10,Fcommunities to come together to stand
OL,11,Fup to suicide."
OL,13,F"We cannot turn a blind eye to the
OL,14,Fnational catastrophe of suicide any
OL,15,Flonger. 6,000 people every year in the
OL,16,FUK alone are being lost to something
OL,17,Fthat is now widely described by expert
OL,18,Fclinicians as preventable."
