OL,3,CAlastair Campbell opens up on mental
OL,4,Chealth at charity conference
OL,6,F"We can either accept the evidence
OL,7,Fthat referrals to mental health
OL,8,Fservices have surged and try as a
OL,9,Fcompassionate society to do something
OL,10,Fpositive about it as a collective or
OL,11,Fwe can dismiss it as part of a "sick
OL,12,Fnote" culture.
OL,14,F"Through our major conference and 2025
OL,15,FBaton tour, we are calling for a sea-
OL,16,Fchange in the UK's complacent and
OL,17,Fneglectful attitude towards suicide
OL,18,Fprevention, aiming to drive collective
OL,19,Faction."
